data.description: Wow! Beautiful 2 story, 4 bedroom home on an oversized partially wooded lot in Vista Woods is now available for you! Upstairs are four welcoming bedrooms, an Owners full bath and second hallway full bathroom, downstairs you'll find a large living room with wood burning fireplace, large eat in kitchen with all appliances included, and a surprisingly spacious laundry room with 1/2 bathroom. The basement is technically unfinished, but outfitted with theatre area and exercise/gaming area. Huge lot for this neighborhood. See this soon and make it yours.
